message.body: Hey you! Isn't your show coming up soon???
I have it in my calendar for next week :)
1/2 Hey!! Yes, it opens the 15th! I'm getting ready for it now. Up till Feb 15. Is that enough time/do you still feel like writing? If not it's totally fine,
Of course I want to write something! Send me info as soon as you can
Omg thanks! Next few days, I promise. You mean like work photos and what else?
Work photos and image list (size dimensions materials years etc) and then we talk on the phone about your work a bit too
